-- India Expects to Sign Shale Gas Technology Agreement During Obama Visit
-- B y   D e b a r a t i   R o y
-- 2010-10-06T15:23:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-06/india-expects-to-sign-shale-gas-technology-agreement-during-obama-visit.html
India expects to sign an agreement
with the U.S. on shale gas technology during President Barack
Obama’s visit to the south Asian country next month, S.
Sundareshan, India’s oil secretary, said in New York today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
